snippet.textDisplay: Tajdar-E-Haram was released almost 9 years ago. I tried to listen to this one a couple of times but couldn’t get the gist of it. Last week I suffered from dengue fever. Now I'm recovering. I have no idea how, somehow Tajdar-E-Haram came up in my head, and now I am listening to this one nonstop all day. Later on, I realised there are some songs(Naat) that will reach you at the right moment; you just have to wait for that moment.
